Empathic Link	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BogunClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural		DESC:A bogun cannot speak, but the process of creating one links it telepathically with its creator. It knows what its creator knows and can convey to him or her everything it sees and hears, up to a range of 1,500 feet. A bogun never travels beyond this range willingly, though it can be removed forcibly. In such a case, it does everything in its power to regain contact with its creator.	KEY:Bogun ~ Empathic Link																											SOURCEPAGE:MM2
																																
###Block: Tricks and Training																																
Companionship	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick.AnimalTrickCompanionship		DESC:Because it is a social creature, a corollax can sometimes be persuaded to accept humanoid companionship on a long-term basis. If a character offers food and makes a successfulHandle Animal check (DC 25 if the character has not previously frightened or abused the bird, or DC 30 otherwise), the corollax considers the character a desirable companion and accompanies him or her willingly in all travels.	KEY:Animal Trick ~ Companionship			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Animal Trick ~ Companionship],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.AnimalTrickCompanionship]	PRERACE:1,Corollax,Companion ~ Corollax																							SOURCEPAGE:MM2
Mimic	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AnimalTrick.AnimalTrickMimic		DESC:These birds are also natural mimics. With a successful Handle Animal check (DC 23), a corollax can be trained to repeat a particular phrase. Each bird is capable of remembering up to nine different phrases, though each phrase requires a separateHandle Animal check.	KEY:Animal Trick ~ Mimic			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Animal Trick ~ Mimic],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.AnimalTrickMimic]	PRERACE:1,Corollax,Companion ~ Corollax																							SOURCEPAGE:MM2
																																
